程序包 org.tron.trident.crypto.tuwenitypes

类 UInt256

java.lang.Object
org.tron.trident.crypto.tuwenitypes.UInt256
所有已实现的接口:
Comparable<UInt256>, UInt256Value<UInt256>
public final class UInt256 extends Object implements UInt256Value<UInt256>
An unsigned 256-bit precision number. This is a raw UInt256Value - a 256-bit precision unsigned number of no particular unit.

    • fromHexString

      public static UInt256 fromHexString(String str)
      Parse a hexadecimal string into a UInt256.
      参数:
      str - The hexadecimal string to parse, which may or may not start with "0x". That representation may contain less than 32 bytes, in which case the result is left padded with zeros.
      返回:
      The value corresponding to str.
      抛出:
      IllegalArgumentException - if str does not correspond to a valid hexadecimal representation or contains more than 32 bytes.

      public UInt256 pow(UInt256 exponent)
      从接口复制的说明: UInt256Value
      Returns a value that is (this<sup>exponent</sup> mod 2<sup>256</sup>)

      This calculates an exponentiation over the modulus of 2^256.

      Note that exponent is an UInt256 rather than of the type T.
